column5: I'm heading up to knee lake in manitoba for the very first time. Anybody ever fish there ? Techniques etc ?
I'm heading up to knee lake in manitoba for the very first time. Anybody ever fish there ? Techniques etc ?
You will catch plenty of fish. Take any bait you can get in the water they all work.
